parameters:
Zerachiel: That mercenary... seems to be
using magic to increase their physical
resistance.

Zerachiel: It seems like we can defeat
them if we use magic.

Zerachiel: That armor looks like it has
high defense... It might be difficult to
defeat them if we don't know any
magic...

Zerachiel: It seems like magic
resistance has been added... Now
fireballs won't work, huh.

Zerachiel: But if it's a powerful impact
technique, it should definitely deal
damage.

Zerachiel: Just one more push, let's do
our best.
Captain: I will avenge my comrades...!
Knight: Captain, I will assist you!
Zerachiel: Are you still coming out...!!

Captain: Puruzou, can you lend me your
strength too...!!

Zerachiel: But I wonder if they're that
person's friend? It might be pitiful to
defeat them...

Knight: You, who have betrayed my
dearest friend...!! I will never forgive
you!!

The captain has activated berserk mode.
Their attack power will greatly increase
until the battle is over.
Priest Soldier B: We will protect you!

Priest Soldier C: Intruders! We won't
let a single finger touch Holy Maiden-
sama!

Zerachiel: I've completely become the
villain...

Knight: Holy maiden, I apologize for the
wait...!

Knight: I will repay the life you saved
by picking me up... right here...!

Captain: All troops, repel the
invaders!!

Zerachiel: The enemy's morale is
rising...! It seems like we should
launch a full-scale attack...!!
Effy: First curse... Ode to Life!

Zerachiel: Ah! My energy is being
drained...!?

Effy: From now on, I will continuously
drain your energy.
Effy: I will make use of your elements.
Effy: It's the Curse of Debilitation.

Effy: With this, it will be difficult
for you to move swiftly.

Zerachiel: But Effy must also be at her
limit, right? She's breathing heavily
through her shoulders.

Zerachiel: (Just one more push... Let's
do our best!!)
Sariel: Remiel...? Why are you here?

Remiel: I was worried about Lord
Sariel...! I want to fight alongside you
too!!

Sariel: You're covered in injuries. You
need to rest.

Remiel: I was originally a failing
student.

Remiel: I was unable to excel in both my
studies and magic, but Lord Sariel was
the only one who saw me...

Remiel: I am not fighting for the
Supreme God. I am fighting for Lord
Sariel!

Sariel: Alright, let's fight together.
But if it gets dangerous, run away.
Remiel: Yes, thank you very much!

Zerachiel: Remiel, that's enough. Step
back.
Sariel: Ahaha, why are you apologizing?

Sariel: ...Thank you for doing that for
me. I'm happy.

Sariel: Leave the rest to me and take a
good rest.

Zerachiel: Remiel is a reliable friend
who supports me.

Sariel: Even though I was injured, you
came to help me.

Sariel: If I don't defeat you all, I
won't be able to face Remiel, will I?

Sariel: Alright, alright! Let's start
the second round!!

Zerachiel: It's fine to fight normally,
but it seems easier to defeat them all
at once with a skill.
Zerachiel: This one... is a Gigas.

Zerachiel: Because she possesses power
that surpasses angels, even if we clash
with our strength, we won't be able to
win.

Zerachiel: In that case... let's use the
\c[6]Dark Wave\c[0].

Zerachiel: If it's the \c[6]Dark
Wave\c[0], we should be able to
withstand the Gigas' attack.
\CLYou should have disposed of it sooner.

\CLYou, as an individual, are different
from any fake body that has ever
existed.

\CLBecause you possess a heart that is
close to that of a human, you could
become a threatening presence to me.

\CLHowever, that's precisely why you are
amazing.

\CLI have finally become complete by
incorporating the Seventh Curse.

\CLWith all my might, I will bring you
despair.

Zerachiel: The elements are going out of
control...

Claudia: Countless billions of elements
are connected, causing the terrain to
collapse...

\CLDefeated by the Emperor of the Ancestors
for a thousand years...

\CLNo matter how time may pass, the thirst
for my revenge will never wane...

\CLThe essence of life is struggle,
survival of the fittest is the
psychology of the world.

\CLThat's why I have chosen the path of
struggle, to dominate the world myself
and quench this thirst.

Rabi: To be able to interact with the
Star Gods...!!

\CLOne giant god challenged the gods and
miraculously survived.

\CLNow, all the power that surpasses even
that giant god has been unleashed.

\CLThe unification of the world is the
beacon of peace.

\CLIf you dare to obstruct me, you shall
perish for eternity.
At that moment, the elements floating in the air were absorbed all at once. The magic power began to go out of control.

In the space dominated by the Seventh
Curse, even the elements residing within
the body are being sucked away.

Furthermore, the body exposed to the
raging waves of elemental energy
gradually decays.

Eden: There is no one who can defy God.
Become a flower blooming in paradise and
wither away, becoming my flesh and
blood.

Zerachiel: ...Now is the time to keep
our promise.

Eden: What I do is nothing more than the
essence of life...

Eden: Even if I were to disappear, and
temporary peace were to come...

Eden: Soon, a new great evil will
appear, and the world will be filled
with chaos...

Eden: This is nothing more than the
prologue to an endless era of war...
Eden: If you continue to resist...

Eden: Keep walking towards the future...
and guide those who hold life...

Eden: Protect the world... and the
important people... with your power...

Eden: ...I have entrusted the world and
the future.
力をためて、即死攻撃を仕掛けてくる。

Claudia: This monster launches powerful
attacks! If you take a direct hit, it's
over!!

Claudia: If the sandworm shows any
strange behavior, it's important to
protect ourselves!!

Zerachiel: Understood! Let's attack when
we find an opening.

Shemini: I won't let you escape, no
way!!

Shemini: The forbidden magic passed down
from the Beast God Anri-sama...!!

Zerachiel: T-the number of people
increased...!!

Claudia: ...None of the elements have
decreased.

Claudia: It means that my abilities
haven't decreased at all.

Shemini: Now...! Please receive my
love!!

Claudia: This should be much tougher
compared to earlier.

Shemini: If it comes to this, I'll use
my last secret plan!!

Shemini: The forbidden magic passed down
from the Beast God Anri-sama, Secret
Art, Part 2...!!
Shemini: It's time to grow gigantic!

Claudia: ...This girl is up for
anything.
Shemini: Now, this is the last one!

Shemini: Please be obedient and become
my partner!!

Shemini: The forbidden magic passed down
from the Beast God, Lord Henri...!!

Zerachiel: The number of people has
increased again...!!

Claudia: ...But just a little more.
Let's settle this in one go.

name: クリーバー＆ウッドノイズ

parameters:
Claudia: Once the ice completely melts,
she'll probably get serious.
Lala: It would be better to prepare.

\CLI was allowed to temporarily leave the
barrier.

\CLNow we can fight to our heart's
content.

Ern: I have been entrusted with the role
of being the guardian of paradise by
that person.

Ern: In the Tree of Dreams, miracles
that will help you won't happen.

Ern: Let me teach you the despair that
surpasses the Star God.

Ern: If you want to save this planet,
show me your true strength and defeat
me.

Seems like you're having a tough time,
Ern...
Ern: That voice... why are you here!?

This is the Great Tree of Fantasia... a
place where memories gather...
I will also help to save the future.

Lala: Claudia, you look just like
her...!!

Lala: Divine Beast Artemis... it's the
counterpart to Marnagarm, right...

You all want to protect your own
world... your paradise, don't you?

If you can't defeat us, you won't be
able to protect the future.

Zerachiel: This element... surpasses the
Star God...!!

Zerachiel: Looks like there's no choice
but to do it!

Sachia: I may be a small existence,
but... I'll protect my friends.

Lala: Goodness... I never expected these
exciting days to continue like this.
Lala: Master Ern, here I go!!
It doesn't matter who you are.
You should walk your own path.

Claudia: ...Yes, I understand. I won't
hesitate anymore.

Claudia: I will carve out the future.
Together with everyone.
Yes, I'll be watching over you.

I, Artemis, the guardian of paradise...
have arrived.
